title: (Fri Full) Blind 90’s Country Karaoke + Lunchbox Slid Into Amy’s Sisters DMs
itunes:title: (Fri Full) Blind 90’s Country Karaoke + Lunchbox Slid Into Amy’s Sisters DMs
description:
The show competes in 90’s country karaoke. We spin the wheel and they have to perform this song it lands on…without the lyrics! Lunchbox slid into Amy’s sisters DMs for a sleazy reason that lead to him calling her for an odd request.
